                  <additions>
                     <p>On f0r and f1r there is annotation which has been heavily crossed out with a black ink pen. This bears the (just visible) name of John Shore and a title page note (f0r) which says "Yusuf u Zulaykha Auctor Firdusi Tusi". On f1r, Jones has written the title of the work underneath the Persian red-ink title page. </p>
